# REPORT.md

## Found

- Health route returns package.json version; RPC/Jito/DB checks present
- Bottom bar wired: StatusCluster and ActionDock mounted in pp/layout.tsx; GlobalHotkeys active (w/g/b/e)
- Routes exist: /wallets, /bundle, /pnl, /trade-history, /spl-creator, /settings
- Wallet groups/roles UI with limits; funding service implements sniper-weighted distribution
- Jito bundle: 20-TX limit; snipers prioritized; tip applied; fallback to RPC
- Sell via Jupiter with feeBps and Raydium fallback stubs; logging in place
- PnL & History: show Gas Fee + Jito Tip; CSV export implemented
- Env: env.example client-safe public endpoints only; server-only secrets via server routes
- Build leak scan: no paid keys in client bundle

## Changed

- helpers/puppeteerHelper.ts: fixed ESLint issues (unnecessary semicolons)
- lib/env.ts: require RPC_URL; optional JITO_RPC_URL; maintain tunables
- components/BundleEngine/BundleEngine.tsx: track per-transaction Gas Fee + Jito Tip in PnL
- app/home/page.tsx: de-dup branding, header now "Dashboard"
- lib/env.ts: align ENV/Zod to mainnet-beta/devnet; add JITO_AUTH_TOKEN; rename PUMP_FUN_API_KEY → PUMPFUN_API_KEY; enforce mainnet requirements
- env.example: aligned names/values; added placeholders only; clarified public vs server-only
- docker-compose.override.yml: removed hardcoded keys; reference .env vars; ensure no paid keys exposed via NEXT_PUBLIC
- app/api/proxy/route.ts: server RPC resolution via helper to avoid composing client RPC from secrets

## Skipped

- Full Raydium SDK pool ops: kept simplified placeholders with clear comments; Jupiter used for swaps
- Deep puppeteer automation credentials wiring: guarded; fallback pathways in place

## Decisions

- Use server /api/proxy for paid integrations (Birdeye/Jupiter/Pump.fun) to avoid client key exposure
- Jito tip distributed evenly across bundle for PnL; gas fee estimated conservatively
- Keep keyboard shortcuts configurable via useSettingsStore; defaults: w/g/b/e
- Keep Jito submission via REST /api/v1/bundles with optional Authorization bearer; fallback to standard RPC on repeated failures
- Normalize network identifiers across app: 'mainnet-beta' | 'devnet'

## Blocked-External

- Local Node.js version is 10.9.2, which is incompatible with Next.js 14 (requires Node >= 18). Please upgrade Node to 20 LTS (or >=18) to proceed with install/build/run. See README for commands or use:
  - winget: `winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS`
  - nvm-windows: `nvm install 20.15.0; nvm use 20.15.0`
